    usf:facetKind facet:uisemantics;
    usf:facetStatus <urn:usf:facetstatus:notapplicable>;
    usf:facetStatement "The semantic compiler exposes no user-interface product surface; its callable automation surface is governed by repository-local commands and machine-readable results.".
